# Aryan Chaudhary Portfolio

A premium personal portfolio website built with Next.js, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Framer Motion.

## Live Website

https://aryanbuilds.vercel.app

## Overview

This portfolio showcases my work, technical skills, experience, and projects in a modern and interactive format. The website is designed with a premium dark theme, smooth animations, responsive layouts, and a developer-focused aesthetic.

## Features

- Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile
- Premium dark UI with glassmorphism effects
- Smooth animations using Framer Motion
- Resume download functionality
- Interactive project showcase
- Experience timeline
- Tech stack section
- Contact section with social links
- Custom signature logo branding
- SEO-friendly structure
- Fast performance with Next.js

