## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/aryanchaudhary22/aryan-chaudhary-portfolio.git
```

Navigate into the project:

```bash
cd aryan-chaudhary-portfolio
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Start development server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

Open:

```bash
http://localhost:3000
```

## Build for Production

```bash
npm run build
```

Run production server:

```bash
npm start
```

